THE WINES OF SPAIN

There is more vineyard land in Spain than in any other country in the world—less than 3% is Sherry. The best table wines are from Rioja and some good ones are produced in Valdepenas—also spot- tily in a few other provinces. Look for the old vintage wines of Rioja which are among the best values in outstanding red wine ex-
